column5: Hey,  I'm going to Jackson's Point tomorrow for the first time, hoping for my first Simcoe Laker/Whitefish.  I was wondering where the nearest bait shop would be?  Also, where does everyone park when heading out of Jackson's Point?  Thanks for any help.
Try Smokeys right down near the launching area. Also there is parking down at the launch.
Hey, thanks for the response.  Do you know by chance what time Smokeys' opens?
